The paper deals with completion and de-noising of video data, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of tensor-SVD and a tensor nuclear norm, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions the use of algorithms for video completion and de-noising, which are topics in multimedia (cs.MM) and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
